unicef-ah6.def: Percentage of women (aged 15-19) who have their need for family planning satisfied with modern methods.
unicef-ah6.name: Demand for family planning satisfied with modern methods, Aged 15-19
unicef-ah6.source: United Nations, Department of Economic and Social Affairs, Population Division (2021). World Contraceptive Use 2021. New York: United Nations; based on Demographic and Health Surveys (DHS), Multiple Indicator Cluster Surveys (MICS), Reproductive Health Surveys, other national surveys, and National Health Information Systems (HIS). Last Update: May 2021.
